## 🤖 Step 5: Model Building & Training
We train 4 models and compare their performance.


======================================== CELL 13 (code) ========================================
# ── Train/Test Split ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
features = ['Year_Num', 'Sales_Lag1', 'Sales_Lag2', 'Rolling_Mean']
X = df_ml[features]
y = df_ml['Sales_Cr']

# Use last 2 years as test
X_train, X_test = X.iloc[:-2], X.iloc[-2:]
y_train, y_test = y.iloc[:-2], y.iloc[-2:]

print(f"Training samples: {len(X_train)} | Test samples: {len(X_test)}")


